deck: A British actor who is most well known his role as Superman in the 2013 Man of Steel movie. He will reprise the role in the upcoming sequel titled Batman vs. Superman: Dawn of Justice.
description:
Comic Related Movie Roles

Superman - Man of Steel (2013), Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice (2016)

Biography

In the 2013 reboot of the Superman film franchise Man of Steel, Cavill played Superman. He had also auditioned for the 2006 film Superman Returns but failed to get the part.

Cavill is set to reprise his role as Superman in the Man of Steel sequel titled Batman vs. Superman: Dawn of Justice alongside Ben Affleck in the role of Batman, Gal Gadot as Wonder Woman, and Jesse Eisenberg in the role of Superman's arch nemesis Lex Luthor.
